1) Introduction

   Any one who used their product know what a pain it was to add
 something to Pascal.Lib, not to mantion of removing units. I found it
 unbeareble to use it, so it is where UnitMover comes in. This program
 was made as a repleacement of LibMaker from HiSoft. It is fully GUI
 driven program to menage Pascal.Lib and units. With this little piece
 of software you can build new library, add units to it remove them (kill),
 save them to disk. This progam also check for integrity of library.

   Unfortunatly this program is not perfect, be this I mean it can only
 work with 2.0+ system. So at least LibMaker has one advantage. If you are
 still pre 2.0 system user do not loos hope (see Future).

